data.description: Don't miss your chance to see this beautiful home on just over 1.6 acres! You will love the open concept of the kitchen, dining, and living areas! Tons of cabinet space, a large, moveable island, a gas fireplace and large pantry are just a few features of the living spaces. Wood look tile throughout most of the home with carpet in the bedrooms! Large primary bedroom includes a walk-in closet, double vanities, jacuzzi tub, walk-in shower AND access to the back patio! You will absolutely fall in love with the country setting this home is surrounded by with plenty of space for chickens and goats or a large garden, all while still being just a short drive to the metro!
